<A>__{as he clicks off, an attractive woman wearing a power suit approaches from the other direction. evan has to look closely, but it's kayleigh. a mature woman, now. he stumbles slightly, caught off guard. as she passes, her eyes linger on his a little longer than necessary, but there's no recognition. evan watches her continue past him and down the sidewalk. after a hesitant beat, he takes a breath, turns around and follows her.}
